            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <h6 class="font-weight-bold">How do I create an account?</h6>
                    <p>To create an account, click on the "Sign Up" button at the top right of the page. Fill in your details, choose a password, and click "Register." You will receive a confirmation email with further instructions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <h6 class="font-weight-bold">How do I reset my password?</h6>
                    <p>If you've forgotten your password, click on the "Forgot Password?" link on the login page. Enter your email address, and you will receive instructions to reset your password.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <h6 class="font-weight-bold">How do I update my account information?</h6>
                    <p>To update your account information, log in and go to your account settings. From there, you can update your email, password, and other personal information.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
